{"title":"刘开渠大师挽词调寄《散余霞》","authors":["赵朴初"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":7,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘开渠大师挽词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调寄《散余霞》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵朴初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔闻谈艺何飞动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不轻传统。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道山西还有老成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要好生留种。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰碑千古高耸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命英雄颂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今观此最后庄严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不禁悲泪涌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）开渠大师手造佛像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乃其一生最后之艺术作品。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}